{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "F74XWLMZ55WFQXLEHJ5FKR7V53B4UBPL",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "020002133",
    "title": "みんなに祝福を",
    "enTitle": "A Smile on Every Face",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "――あのね、トレーナーさん。",
            "enText": "Hey, Trainer?",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 62,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": 940083461620449412,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "もう1つ、ご褒美のお願い、聞いてもらってもいいかな……？",
            "enText": "I was wondering... Could you treat me one<n>more time?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 151,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -1089667596445854685,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "ライス、小さいとき、よく絵本を読んでたの。\r\n絵本を読んで、初めて夢を叶えたいって思ったの。",
            "enText": "You see, when I was little, I read a lot of<n>picture books. They taught\nme how to<n>dream.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 307,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -9075852438458271209,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "だから、今度はライスの番。\r\nみんなに夢を届ける、そんな絵本を書いてみたいなって――",
            "enText": "So now it's my turn. I want to make a<n>picture book that'll inspire\nothers to<n>dream.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 328,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": 8625056030140460389,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――真っ暗に空が荒れ、嵐の日が長らく続いていました。\n山も怒ったように強い風が吹き荒れ、震えています。",
            "enText": "The skies became dark, and storms raged<n>on for days and days.\nViolent winds<n>bellowed down from the mountains as they<n>shook with\nanger.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 328,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -5933082350359324030,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『いつまでも荒れ続ける怖い天気を、青空に変えて欲しい』",
            "enText": "\"I wish someone would make the scary<n>weather go away and give us\nclear skies.\"",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 160,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -5291709104942233354,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "誰もがそう願っていたとき、魔法使いが姿を見せました。",
            "enText": "The people all made the same wish, and<n>that's when the witch\nappeared.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 165,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -2681266549487366652,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "魔法使いはみんなに見守られる中、覚悟を決めて魔法を使います。",
            "enText": "As they all looked on expectantly, the<n>witch summoned her courage\nand cast a<n>spell.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 203,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": 3763121779861646794,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "すると、やさしい風が吹き、一瞬で空が晴れました。",
            "enText": "A gentle breeze began to blow, and the<n>clouds parted in an instant.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 173,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -3174961430478144666,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "山も青く、透き通るような綺麗な風があたりに流れました。",
            "enText": "The mountains regained their lush green,<n>and the air grew crisp and\nfresh.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 195,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -3417710978695654476,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "みんなはとても喜んで、魔法使いを歓迎しました。",
            "enText": "The people rejoiced and welcomed the<n>witch.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 148,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": 1382580299119989381,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『わたしの力は、このためにあったんだ』",
            "enText": "\"So this is why I have these powers!\"",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -7717374772686443869,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "魔法使いは人々に笑顔で応えました。",
            "enText": "The witch returned their greetings with a<n>smile.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": -3635101308717161193,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こうして魔法使いは、青くて大きい空の下、\nいつまでもいつまでも……。",
            "enText": "And so the witch continued her travels<n>under that big blue sky,\nforever and ever...",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 222,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": 6054401936245903380,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "みんなを幸せにする魔法をかけていきました――",
            "enText": "Using her magic to bring happiness<n>everywhere she went.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 229,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "voiceSheetId": "020002133",
            "pathId": 2385695713438800845,
            "blockIdx": 15
        }
    ]
}